headline: Travelers Launches Industry-Leading Agentic AI Claim Assistant Developed with OpenAI
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., February 18, 2026--The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE: TRV) today announced the launch of AI Claim Assistant, an industry-leading solution developed using OpenAI model capabilities and APIs. The fully agentic intelligent voice service uses advanced language and speech recognition technologies to handle customer claim calls. headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Consider Right Now and 2 We Find Risky
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
